item.description:
We will meet at 7pm for dinner at Byblos Restaurant in Norwood. Check out their website at: Byblos Restaurant website
Everyone pays for their own food/drinks.

Have fun enjoying new food, catching up with friends and meeting other new, friendly people.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo). I'll be carrying a large red purse. If you have trouble finding us, call 774 232 0000.
item.why: Join us for great Middle Eastern food, drinks and good times with fun and outgoing people!
